</li><li class="c-issue-toc__article c-issue-toc__article--has-translation" data-aricle-no="01">
	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="1801"><a href="/pl/archiwum/2018/22-zobaczyc-antropocen/natura-jako-kurator">Natura jako kurator. Dziedzictwo kulturowe w epoce antropocenu</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Autorka:--><a href="/pl/bio?id=1812">Monika Stobiecka</a></h5>
	
			<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi1801" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary1801" data-lexicon-show="pokaż" data-lexicon-hide="ukryj">
